    "en": {
      "title": "Four babies in one delivery",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "For the first time in the history of Puttalam Hospital, a woman has given birth to four children in one delivery.",
        "A 24-year-old young mother gave birth to these children, said Puttalam Hospital Director Dr. Sumit Enton Fernando.",
        "At present, the four children concerned are receiving safe treatment under the supervision of Pediatrician Dr. Surin Jayawardena of Puttalam Aadar Hospital.(R)"
      ],
